      <hint/>
      <answer/>
      <solution>
        <p>
          Since <m>\cot(t) = \cos(t)/\sin(t)</m>, the cotangent values for Q1–Q2 are: <m>u, \sqrt{3}, 1, \frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}, 0, -\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}, -1, -\sqrt{3}, u</m>; and for Q3–Q4: <m>\sqrt{3}, 1, \frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}, 0, -\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}, -1, -\sqrt{3}, u</m>.
        </p>
      </solution>
